pageProduct.name: Swisse Skincare Hemp Seed Gentle Cream Cleanser 100ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Skincare Hemp Seed Gentle Cream Cleanser is luxuriously formulated with raw, cold-pressed, 100% Australian Hemp Seed Oil, and Macadamia Seed Oil to gently cleanse and replenish the skin. It removes make-up and impurities whilst leaving the skin feeling soft, supple and hydrated.

Warnings

This product contains essential oils. Test prior to use. In the unlikely event of a negative reaction, consult your medical practitioner. Store below 25°C.

Ingredients

Water, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycol Stearate, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil, Glycerin (Plant Derived), Macadamia Ternifolia (Macadamia) Seed Oil, Decyl Glucoside, Phenoxyethanol, Coco-Glucoside, Cannabis Sativa (Hemp) Seed Oil, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Ceteareth-20, Neopentyl Glycol Diheptanoate, Isododecane, Honey (Manuka), Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Oil, Citrus Bergamia (Bergamot) Peel Oil Expressed, Cinnamomum Zeylanicum (Cinnamon) Leaf Oil, Citrus Bergamia (Bergamot) Peel Oil Expressed, Eucalyptus Globulus Leaf Oil, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Chloride, Fragrance, Linalool, Limonene, Geraniol, Eugenol.87.0% naturally derived ingredients. 87.0% naturally derived ingredients.

Directions

Blend a small amount between palms and massage onto wet skin in a circular motion. Rinse with warm water. Use twice daily in the morning and evening.
